{"code":200,"msg":"success","data":[{"id":243,"createTime":"2019-06-03 10:26:58","topicId":null,"tagId":51,"rule":4,"weight":1,"sort":1,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p style=\"line-height:24px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">心悸</span></strong></p><table><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9); border-width: 1px; border-style: solid;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、病因诱因：心率异常、心律失常、心脏搏动增强及心搏量增加、心脏神经官能症</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、主要症状特点：心悸病程、性质（间歇性或阵发性）？发作频率？持续时间？缓解因素？进展情况？与体力活动关系？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、伴随症状：是否伴心前区疼痛不适、呼吸困难、咳嗽咳痰、头痛头晕、发热、感染、多汗、消瘦、失血？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、全身状态：发病以来饮食、睡眠、大小便及体重变化</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、诊疗经过：发病以来是否到医院检查过，（心电图、Holter、心脏彩超、甲状腺功能）曾做过哪些检查和治疗？治疗是否有效？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、相关病史：(1)有无药物过敏史、手术史</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">(2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">既往有无类似病史？有无高血压病、各种心脏病、慢性呼吸系统疾病、贫血、甲亢及神经官能症？有无烟酒嗜好？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"","topic":null,"options":[],"tags":[{"id":289,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 16:03:45","updateTime":"2019-06-01 16:03:45","name":"心悸","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":19},{"id":51,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 13:45:51","updateTime":"2019-06-01 13:45:51","name":"心悸","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":15}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}